JOYFUL DEPARTURE bumped with horse to her outside at the start, settled in the middle of the pack on the inside for the run up the backstretch, saved ground around the bend and improved position in the stretch. WIN FOR LAILA brushed with the horse to her inside at the start, raced in the middle of the pack between horses through the early going, came around the turn in the two path and chased on to the wire. CAUSE I'M ELEGANT veered in and bumped with the horse to his outside at the break, raced off the pace early, saved ground around the turn, began a bid passing the quarter pole and gained ground mildly in the lane. DUSTED bumped with the horse to her inside at the start, settled at the back of the pack on the inside through the opening stages, navigated the bend from the three path and never threatened. SECRET SPELL raced in the middle of the pack between horses early, continued around the turn in the two path and showed no kick. GEMINI WARRIOR bumped with the horse to her outside at the gate, tracked the leader on the inside up the backstretch, navigated the bend from the three path and tired in the lane. CHIMING IN hit the gate leaving it, raced in the middle of the pack on the outside up the backstretch, came around the turn in the four path and faded in the stretch. FLIRTING bumped with the horse to her outside at the break, raced off the pace through the opening stages, swung out to the four path coming around the bend, and was empty in the lane. DUE TO A STARTING GATE MALFUNCTION, HORSE TWELVE, CRYSTAL THE PISTOL, WAS DECLARED A NON STARTER.
